<coordinates>121.138064,24.549746,919</coordinates>
</Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name><![CDATA[0844林道終點，右側雜木緩坡找路下切小溝，方向正南。]]></name>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.13824</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.548815</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 899 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T00:44:54Z</td></tr></table>
]]>
</description>
<TimeStamp>
<when>2023-11-11T00:44:54Z</when>
</TimeStamp>
<styleUrl>#waypoint</styleUrl>
<Point>
<altitudeMode>clampToGround</altitudeMode>
<coordinates>121.13824,24.548815,899</coordinates>
</Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name><![CDATA[0907小溝轉乾溪溝，石溝中出現兩米石面落差，有拉繩。]]></name>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.138158</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.548426</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 860 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T01:07:32Z</td></tr></table>
]]>
</description>
<TimeStamp>
<when>2023-11-11T01:07:32Z</when>
</TimeStamp>
<styleUrl>#waypoint</styleUrl>
<Point>
<altitudeMode>clampToGround</altitudeMode>
<coordinates>121.138158,24.548426,860</coordinates>
</Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name><![CDATA[0934拉繩降至芒草區，發現疑似林道。對岸無破口，往下游方向移動找下溪點。鑽芒草叢後，可見對岸石壁，此案上游處的石壁邊邊有不用架繩便可下至溪底的路。]]></name>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.137983</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.548066</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 850 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T01:33:46Z</td></tr></table>
]]>
</description>
<TimeStamp>
<when>2023-11-11T01:33:46Z</when>
</TimeStamp>
<styleUrl>#waypoint</styleUrl>
<Point>
<altitudeMode>clampToGround</altitudeMode>
<coordinates>121.137983,24.548066,850</coordinates>
</Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name><![CDATA[1010下切至溪底小沙洲，左側可見深潭，右側則為水深到腳踝的過溪處，有人在上游釣魚，休息。對岸可見兩道石壁中間的崩溝，疑似可以攀溝上稜。]]></name>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.137779</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.547943</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 821 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T02:15:56Z</td></tr></table>
]]>
</description>
<TimeStamp>
<when>2023-11-11T02:15:56Z</when>
</TimeStamp>
<styleUrl>#waypoint</styleUrl>
<Point>
<altitudeMode>clampToGround</altitudeMode>
<coordinates>121.137779,24.547943,821</coordinates>
</Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name><![CDATA[1033過溪，水深小腿肚。整裝後決定架繩攻擊乾溝。]]></name>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.137556</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.54793</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 803 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T02:33:45Z</td></tr></table>
]]>
</description>
<TimeStamp>
<when>2023-11-11T02:33:45Z</when>
</TimeStamp>
<styleUrl>#waypoint</styleUrl>
<Point>
<altitudeMode>clampToGround</altitudeMode>
<coordinates>121.137556,24.54793,803</coordinates>
</Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name><![CDATA[1315架繩沿崩勾上至崩溝中的烏龜島，之後在從烏龜島的瘦稜上切至主稜。整條崩溝與上切路徑的地面破碎，落石巨大且多，風險大，並不適合作為路線行走。建議在溪底時便往下游繞掉崩溝下游的岩壁，找稜尾上切。]]></name>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.137559</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.547535</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 867 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T05:15:44Z</td></tr></table>
]]>
</description>
<TimeStamp>
<when>2023-11-11T05:15:44Z</when>
</TimeStamp>
<styleUrl>#waypoint</styleUrl>
<Point>
<altitudeMode>clampToGround</altitudeMode>
<coordinates>121.137559,24.547535,867</coordinates>
</Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name><![CDATA[1405舒適不寬樹根稜線。]]></name>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.138075</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.54712</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 908 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T06:05:00Z</td></tr></table>
