<![CDATA[
<table><tr><td>Longitude: 121.138033</td></tr><tr><td>Latitude: 24.546091</td></tr><tr><td>Altitude: 957 M</td></tr><tr><td>Time: 2023-11-11T06:19:37Z</td></tr></table>
